<string_table>
	<!-- ASSAULT TERRITORY 1 FOR MONOLITH LEADER TASK -->
	<string id="pri_monolith_monolith_trader_stalker_task_1_name"><text>歼灭敌人</text></string>
	<string id="pri_monolith_monolith_trader_stalker_task_1_text"><text>履行黑石的职责. 工作做完后向兔子汇报.</text></string>
	<string id="pri_monolith_monolith_trader_stalker_task_1_about"><text>我有一个重要的使命要交给你. 你需要进入这块区域, 并碾死那些蝼蚁, 准备好了吗?.</text></string>
	<string id="pri_monolith_monolith_trader_stalker_task_1_finish"><text>任务完成了?好.赞美许愿石.</text></string>

	<!-- ASSAULT TERRITORY 2 FOR MONOLITH LEADER TASK -->
	<string id="pri_monolith_monolith_trader_stalker_task_2_name"><text>哒蒙娜丽</text></string>
	<string id="pri_monolith_monolith_trader_stalker_task_2_text"><text>有潜行者试图关闭焦脑器.杀了他.</text></string>
	<string id="pri_monolith_monolith_trader_stalker_task_2_about"><text>有人对我们的伟大事业造成了许多威胁. 有一个人试图再次关闭焦脑器. 千万不能让他得逞. 你必须找到并杀掉他.</text></string>
	<string id="pri_monolith_monolith_trader_stalker_task_2_finish"><text>蒙娜丽邀请你去他房间一趟.</text></string>

	<!-- ASSAULT TERRITORY 3 FOR MONOLITH LEADER TASK -->
	<string id="pri_monolith_monolith_trader_stalker_task_3_name"><text>找到%s</text></string>
	<string id="pri_monolith_monolith_trader_stalker_task_3_text"><text>兔子需要一支新的步枪来加强黑石部队</text></string>
	<string id="pri_monolith_monolith_trader_stalker_task_3_about"><text>我们一天比一天强大. 我们需要更多的武器来实现我们的目标.你必须找到一把新的武器, 让我们继续填充我们的军械库.</text></string>
	<string id="pri_monolith_monolith_trader_stalker_task_3_finish"><text>成功了吗? 很好. 赞美黑石. </text></string>

	<!-- ASSAULT TERRITORY 4 FOR MONOLITH LEADER TASK -->
	<string id="pri_monolith_monolith_trader_stalker_task_4_name"><text>野味</text></string>
	<string id="pri_monolith_monolith_trader_stalker_task_4_text"><text>带来%s. </text></string>
	<string id="pri_monolith_monolith_trader_stalker_task_4_about"><text>去特异区狩猎%s, 以便你的黑石兄弟可以饱餐一顿.</text></string>
	<string id="pri_monolith_monolith_trader_stalker_task_4_finish"><text>成功了吗? 很好. 赞美黑石. </text></string>

