	<string id="pri_monolith_monolith_trader_stalker_task_5_name"><text>找到%s</text></string>
	<string id="pri_monolith_monolith_trader_stalker_task_5_text"><text>找到%s 并把它们给兔子</text></string>
	<string id="pri_monolith_monolith_trader_stalker_task_5_about"><text>你一定要采购更多的物资, 让我们完成更伟大的工作.</text></string>
	<string id="pri_monolith_monolith_trader_stalker_task_5_finish"><text>你做得很好. 弟兄们以你为荣. </text></string>

