    <string id="pri_monolith_monolith_trader_stalker_task_6_name"><text>找到%s </text></string>
    <string id="pri_monolith_monolith_trader_stalker_task_6_text"><text>寻找%s. 把它带给兔子, </text></string>
    <string id="pri_monolith_monolith_trader_stalker_task_6_about"><text>我们必须找到一个神器. 来为使黑石变得更强大效力.</text></string>
    <string id="pri_monolith_monolith_trader_stalker_task_6_fetch_about"><text>你找到了一个%s.我们会为你举行仪式的</text></string>
    <string id="pri_monolith_monolith_trader_stalker_task_6_fetch_finish"><text>你为黑石做了很多不错的事. 今晚会有新人加入我们的仪式.你可能需要上去演讲.</text></string> 

	<!-- FIND MUTANT MEAT FOR MONOLITH LEADER TASK -->
	<string id="pri_monolith_monolith_trader_stalker_task_7_name"><text>为兔子寻找野味肉</text></string>
	<string id="pri_monolith_monolith_trader_stalker_task_7_text"><text>狩猎并现场处理%s. 将肉带回给兔子烹制. </text></string>
	<string id="pri_monolith_monolith_trader_stalker_task_7_about"><text>我们的补给不足. 你必须进入特异区猎取肉食, 让黑石的弟兄们得以饱餐. </text></string>
	<string id="pri_monolith_monolith_trader_stalker_task_7_fetch_about"><text>%c[ui_8]去狩猎并带回%c[ui_orange]%s%c[default]. 记住这些生物是特异区的恩赐. 迅速击杀并心怀感恩. 成功后把肉带给我. </text></string>
	<string id="pri_monolith_monolith_trader_stalker_task_7_fetch_finish"><text>你成功完成了任务. 干得好. </text></string>

