	<string id="pri_monolith_monolith_mechanic_stalker_task_3_fetch_about"><text>我需要一套校准工具.有了它我能干的事就多了.如果你能给我带一套回来, 我将不胜感激,今后你来我这都给你打折.</text></string>
	<string id="pri_monolith_monolith_mechanic_stalker_task_3_fetch_finish"><text>好.把他们放这吧.</text></string>

